 to the entropy density as large as $\\sim 10^{-10}$,\nwhich is consistent with the observational data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 24 Jul 2021 03:56:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2022 09:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
